# PennyPlay — backend & payments wiring (optional)
#
# Leave everything unset to run in local demo mode (all data stays on the
# device and Plus runs in clearly-labelled test mode).
#
# ── Supabase ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a project at https://supabase.com (or `supabase projects create`)
# 2. Apply the migrations in supabase/migrations/ (`supabase db push`)
# 3. Deploy the edge functions:
#      supabase functions deploy award-xp
#      supabase functions deploy payfast-checkout
#      supabase functions deploy payfast-itn --no-verify-jwt
#      supabase functions deploy payfast-cancel
# 4. Copy this file to .env and fill in the values from your project's API settings
#
# Project: BUDGET (ewvaykmaoxcumkmrjvkm, eu-central-2)
# Use the publishable key (sb_publishable_…) or legacy anon key for VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://ewvaykmaoxcumkmrjvkm.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# ── PayFast (server-side — set as EDGE FUNCTION secrets, not here) ──────
# PennyPlay Plus is a yearly auto-renewing PayFast subscription (R200/year).
# The payment rails are configured on the Supabase functions, never in the
# client bundle.
#
# DEFAULT (no secrets set): the functions use PayFast's public sandbox
# merchant (10000100 / 46f0cd694581a / jt7NOE43FZPn) on
# sandbox.payfast.co.za — full checkout works end to end, no real money.
#
# GO LIVE — set your own merchant account (dashboard → Settings →
# Integration) as edge function secrets:
#
#   supabase secrets set PAYFAST_MERCHANT_ID=your-merchant-id
#   supabase secrets set PAYFAST_MERCHANT_KEY=your-merchant-key
#   supabase secrets set PAYFAST_PASSPHRASE=your-salt-passphrase   # REQUIRED for yearly auto-renew
#   # optional: PAYFAST_SANDBOX=1 to run YOUR keys against the sandbox
#
# The passphrase must match the "Salt Passphrase" on your PayFast account.
# Yearly auto-renew REQUIRES it — PayFast rejects unsigned subscription
# requests.

# ── PayFast (legacy client fallback — optional) ─────────────────────────
# Only used when the payfast-checkout edge function isn't deployed. Prefer
# the server path (required for a real auto-renewing subscription).
#VITE_PAYFAST_MERCHANT_ID=
#VITE_PAYFAST_MERCHANT_KEY=
#VITE_PAYFAST_SANDBOX=1
